Available Tools: get_weather_alerts | get_storm_warnings | get_air_quality_index
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "severity": "string" }
Response Schema: { "alerts": [{ "type": "string", "severity": "string", "message": "string", "expires": "string" }] }
---
Question: Are there any heat advisories currently active for Phoenix?
Call: { "func_call": "get_weather_alerts", "location": "Phoenix, AZ", "severity": "high" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Excessive Heat Warning", "severity": "high", "message": "Dangerously hot conditions with temperatures up to 115F expected. Drink plenty of fluids and stay in air-conditioned rooms.", "expires": "2024-05-22T20:00:00Z" }] }

Question: Check for hurricane warnings along the Gulf Coast in Mobile.
Call: { "func_call": "get_storm_warnings", "location": "Mobile, AL", "severity": "extreme" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Hurricane Warning", "severity": "extreme", "message": "Life-threatening storm surge and damaging winds expected within 36 hours. Evacuate immediately if ordered.", "expires": "2024-05-23T06:00:00Z" }] }

Question: I need to know if there are high wind warnings affecting Albuquerque.
Call: { "func_call": "get_weather_alerts", "location": "Albuquerque, NM", "severity": "moderate" }
